snippet.title: Game & Watch - Zelda (c)1989 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: This is Nintendo's Zelda, from the Game & Watch series, running in MAME.  Zelda was the penultimate Game & Watch title.  Emulation by algestam and will be supported in MAME 0.209.  The background artwork was provided by hydef and can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1IbSRYTfKoKDgZfJZTZdnKFSpBvCvgJZV
